								<p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: normal; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;"><a href="<?=$user->getFastauthUrl('http://runet-id.com/user/edit/')?>" class="btn-primary" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; color: #FFF; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; background: #2F8EDC; margin: 0 10px 0 0; padding: 0; border-color: #2f8edc; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 40px;">АКТУАЛИЗИРОВАТЬ ПРОФИЛЬ</a></p>
